ai-patthana15.29:0.2_0: The Order of the Dhamma: allows unintelligent in the Khadehaka, and constantly preciously,
ai-patthana15.29:1.1_0: I don’t give rise to skillful qualities. Please don’t give rise to the cause or condition.
ai-patthana15.29:2.1_0: I didn’t give rise to unskillful things or formless.
ai-patthana15.29:3.1_0: I haven’t declared that form is in line with the teaching.
